(firstQuint)Comparative Efficacy and Tolerability of No7 in Osteoarthritis of the Knee.

 Solgar No7 is a Dietary Supplement marketed in Israel on a regular basis with the approval of the Israeli Ministry of Health.

 The product is based on Herbal Extracts and Vitamins.

 The individual components of the product were effective in some studies in relieving pain and inflammation in such patients.

 This Study evaluates the effect of these components as a complex.

